article.headline: Missouri St. 78, UNC Wilmington 62
article.story: WILMINGTON, N.C. (AP) -- Blake Ahearn led five players in double-digit scoring with 18 points as Missouri State defeated UNC Wilmington 78-62 on Saturday. Nathan Bilyeu added 15 points and nine rebounds and Tyler Chaney scored 12 and had eight rebounds for the Bears (8-1). Dale Lamberth came off the bench to score 11 points and Spencer Laurie posted 10. The Bears made 14 of 26 shots from beyond the arc (53.8 percent) and led 39-31 at the break. Daniel Fountain scored 13 points and Montez Downey added 12 for the Seahawks (3-5), who shot just 33.9 percent from the field.
